## 3. Team Name Conventions

### Naming Hierarchy
| Priority | Type | Example |
|----------|------|---------|
| Primary | Canonical full name | "UCLA Bruins", "Alabama Crimson Tide" |
| Secondary | Short name / Alias | "UCLA", "Alabama", "Bama", "Roll Tide" |

### Rules
- Store and display **canonical names** as the primary identifier
- Allow short names and aliases for search and user input
- Use case-insensitive matching for duplicate detection
- Strip athletic suffixes ("Bruins", "Tigers", etc.) when checking for duplicates

